These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, police-officer, dancer, firefighter, dressmaker, bartender, scientist
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, turkish, malaysian, british, indian, indonesian, american
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the british##1
 2. the indian is the firefighter##1
 3. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1
 4. the malaysian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 5. the dancer is in the middle##1
 6. the dutch is on the far left##1
 7. the dressmaker is the dutch##1
 8. the analyst is on the right of the indonesian##1
 9. the malaysian is on the left of the turkish##1
10. the british is on the left of the dancer##1
11. the scientist is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | dressmaker | firefighter | police-officer | dancer | analyst | bartender | scientist |
| Nationality   | dutch    | indian   | british      | indonesian | malaysian    | turkish    | american         |

