.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pomegranate, carrot, grapes, banana, avocado, kiwi, grapefruit
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: salsa, indie, hip-hop, country, disco, metal, techno
 1. the fan of disco is the person eating banana##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 3. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of country##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 7. the fan of disco is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 9. the fan of techno is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
10. the person eating banana is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | pomegranate | carrot | avocado | banana | kiwi | grapefruit | grapes |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | hip-hop   | country   | disco      | salsa       | techno       | metal     |

