.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: strawberry, grapes, broccoli, potato, apple, kale, papaya
The people have 7 different jobs:  musician, chef, videographer, doctor, dressmaker, firefighter, lawyer
 1. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 2. the person eating apple is on the left of the lawyer##1
 3. the chef is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 5. the musician is the person eating apple##1
 6. the videographer is on the right of the chef##1
 7. the chef is on the left of the videographer##1
 8. the chef is on the right of the doctor##1
 9. the person eating kale is the doctor##1
10. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the musician##1
11. the doctor is in the middle##1
12. the person eating papaya is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | grapes | apple     | broccoli  | kale       | strawberry       | papaya  | potato   |
| Job    | firefighter  | musician | lawyer | doctor | chef | videographer | dressmaker |

