.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: punk, hip-hop, dubstep, blues, country, house, d&b
There are 7 different nationalities: british, spanish, canadian, brazilian, turkish, chinese, russian
 1. the fan of country is the spanish##1
 2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of house##1
 3. the chinese is on the right of the canadian##1
 4. the british is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of house is on the far left##1
 7. the canadian is on the right of the fan of house##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the chinese##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is the turkish##1
10. the turkish is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the russian is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | house    | d&b     | blues     | dubstep      | hip-hop | country      | punk     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | canadian | chinese | turkish | russian | spanish | british |

