.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, camping, collecting, traveling, rock-climbing, woodworking, hiking
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird, mouse, rat, rabbit, hamster, lizard
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | camping | collecting | woodworking     | traveling | hiking | rock-climbing | skydiving |
| Pet     | lizard   | mouse    | rabbit | hamster     | chinchilla         | rat     | bird        |

