.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, mirinda, fanta, tea, water, milk
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, airplane, bike, boat, scooter, helicopter, motorbike
 1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the van##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | water   | lemonade | fanta | milk  | tea | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | boat   | scooter | van | helicopter     | airplane | motorbike | bike   |

