.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, action, zombie, documentary, superhero, family, scientific
The people use 7 different means of transport: ship, scooter, car, bike, subway, van, airplane
 1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | scientific | documentary | superhero | family     | action | zombie |
| Transport     | van | bike      | airplane | car    | subway | scooter   | ship  |

