.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: pear, artichoke, lemon, onion, raspberry, plum, peas
The people use 7 different means of transport: trike, bus, car, train, taxi, snowmobile, scooter
 1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
