 4. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
 5. the person driving the train is the person eating pear##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is the person eating plum##1
 7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
