 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
