.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-15::.
There 7 different types of food: cabbage, peas, cauliflower, pineapple, mango, cherry, cranberry
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, lacrosse, skateboarding, swimming, skiing, golf
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating cherry is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 8. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
11. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6     |      7       |
| Food    | peas | cauliflower | cranberry     | cabbage | pineapple | cherry | mango       |
| Sport   | surfing | skateboarding | lacrosse | swimming     | golf  | volleyball  | skiing |

